6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Figma AI and Framer share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Brand Kit, Ai Generation. Interestingly, both platforms offer nearly identical feature sets. The difference lies more in the implementation quality and depth of each feature rather than feature availability itself. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Figma AI holds an overall score of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Framer scores 8/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Figma AI and Framer offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Figma AI's free tier and Framer's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
